Privacy Policy
We have an open and upfront policy on data storage. Currently, we do not require or store any user data on our servers.
We need to keep track of bookmark, history, and settings for game types/questions. This information is not stored on our servers but is stored on a users local device.
Third Party Services
Revenuecat: We use a service called Revenuecat for in app purchases. Revenuecat stores your purchase history so we can back up purchases if needed. No other user information is required.
