Terms of Service
1. Introduction
Welcome to Good Chat. These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the Good Chat mobile application ("App"). By using the App, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the App.
2. Use of the App
The App is provided for entertainment purposes and to help users engage in better conversations through a game format.
The App offers both free and subscription-based access to various question types.
3. User Data
Good Chat does not collect or store any user data. The App pulls in questions from an external database to present to users in a game format.
4. Subscriptions
The App includes a subscription service to access premium question types.
Subscriptions are billed monthly, and payments are processed through the App Store.
You can manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal by going to your Account Settings after purchase.
